00:02:07.870 --> 00:02:09.360
I have looked for many cooks

00:02:09.360 --> 00:02:10.430
and tried many methods.

00:02:10.840 --> 00:02:12.960
But they can't recreate your taste.

00:02:13.400 --> 00:02:15.680
What exactly did you put in it?

00:02:16.870 --> 00:02:18.000
To make Bird's Nest Porridge,

00:02:18.470 --> 00:02:21.240
