00:02:22.960 --> 00:02:24.120
If you like to drink it,

00:02:24.280 --> 00:02:25.840
I can make it for you again.

00:02:26.310 --> 00:02:28.360
Wouldn't that be too much trouble
for you?

00:02:29.150 --> 00:02:31.520
I usually make it for myself as well.

00:02:32.030 --> 00:02:34.360
I'll send you a bowl
when the time comes.

00:02:36.680 --> 00:02:37.710
Thank you, Mother.

00:03:27.630 --> 00:03:28.520
Wanning.

00:03:28.630 --> 00:03:29.470
Mother.

00:03:30.400 --> 00:03:31.470
What's wrong, Wanning?

00:03:31.520 --> 00:03:32.470
Mother.

00:03:33.400 --> 00:03:34.360
Do you want to drink it?

00:03:34.360 --> 00:03:36.000
I do, Mother.

00:03:37.150 --> 00:03:37.990
How about this?

00:03:38.470 --> 00:03:40.710
First, hand over the house key

00:03:40.710 --> 00:03:42.630
you took from me.

00:03:43.100 --> 00:03:44.840
From now on, I'll make it for you
every day.

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:46.840
Alright.

00:03:49.280 --> 00:03:50.120
Here, Mother.

00:03:51.330 --> 00:03:52.330
There is one more matter.

00:03:52.520 --> 00:03:54.000
Did Commander Pei come to our house

00:03:54.190 --> 00:03:56.150
to investigate Hongzhen Incense?

00:03:59.150 --> 00:04:00.360
If you don't tell me,

00:04:00.840 --> 00:04:03.680
you won't get to drink this porridge.

00:04:05.360 --> 00:04:06.310
I'll tell you, Mother.

00:04:06.750 --> 00:04:08.590
He came here to investigate it.

00:04:08.710 --> 00:04:09.750
And he said

00:04:09.750 --> 00:04:11.030
you have Hongzhen Incense.

00:04:12.400 --> 00:04:15.150
Could you help me with something?

00:04:25.920 --> 00:04:27.310
Many thanks to you, Commander Pei.

00:04:27.950 --> 00:04:30.070
We will be counting
on your care and support

00:04:30.310 --> 00:04:31.360
in the future.

00:04:32.160 --> 00:04:33.510
Lady Xu, you are too polite.

00:04:47.560 --> 00:04:48.400
Please.

00:05:17.630 --> 00:05:18.560
Wanning,

00:05:18.800 --> 00:05:20.950
you really have not let me down.

00:05:21.240 --> 00:05:22.560
Since he wants to investigate us,

00:05:23.040 --> 00:05:24.950
then let him be addicted
to Hongzhen Incense

00:05:25.600 --> 00:05:26.800
and go to hell himself.

00:05:30.120 --> 00:05:31.040
Mother.

00:05:33.430 --> 00:05:34.360
Mother,

00:05:34.950 --> 00:05:36.750
give me another bowl
of Bird's Nest Porridge.

00:05:39.390 --> 00:05:40.430
Wanning,

00:05:40.720 --> 00:05:43.160
I will give you something even better.

00:05:44.270 --> 00:05:45.360
Alright.

00:06:00.630 --> 00:06:02.160
It turns out

00:06:03.040 --> 00:06:04.560
you place Hongzhen Incense here.

00:06:10.510 --> 00:06:12.680
It is truly not easy

00:06:13.870 --> 00:06:15.190
to let you hand it over.

00:06:16.430 --> 00:06:17.360
You all...

00:06:18.240 --> 00:06:19.830
You are actually deceiving me.

00:06:23.940 --> 00:06:24.500
Do you know

00:06:24.500 --> 00:06:26.670
the consequences of being addicted
to Hongzhen incense?

00:06:27.680 --> 00:06:28.520
I know.

00:06:28.700 --> 00:06:30.660
Every time I drink it,
I immediately spit it out.

00:06:31.000 --> 00:06:32.690
There really is Hongzheng Incense
in here?

00:06:36.360 --> 00:06:37.560
That's what I was thinking.

00:06:37.830 --> 00:06:39.630
Since Lady Cui used Hongzhen Incense
on me,

00:06:39.800 --> 00:06:41.460
then let's simply play along
with her plan

00:06:41.680 --> 00:06:43.000
and lure her into handing it over.

00:06:49.770 --> 00:06:50.990
Since you've made up your mind,

00:06:51.600 --> 00:06:52.560
then go ahead and do it.

00:06:52.950 --> 00:06:54.370
But your life is the most important.

00:06:55.190 --> 00:06:56.070
Don't worry.

00:06:56.480 --> 00:06:58.190
Now I have Ruyi and Chang'an.

00:06:58.390 --> 00:06:59.830
I do value my own life.

00:07:01.430 --> 00:07:02.510
Alright.

00:07:03.160 --> 00:07:05.430
You really have made
a grand strategic move.

00:07:05.680 --> 00:07:07.560
Even I was deceived.

00:07:08.430 --> 00:07:10.630
But how did you know

00:07:10.800 --> 00:07:13.270
that I would believe you were addicted
to Hongzhen Incense?

00:07:13.600 --> 00:07:15.340
Once a person reaches the end
of their rope,

00:07:15.340 --> 00:07:16.170
they become anxious

00:07:16.210 --> 00:07:18.290
and anxiety can easily cause them
to lose composure.

00:07:19.720 --> 00:07:21.390
However, you're indeed wise.

00:07:21.750 --> 00:07:24.720
I had to put in a lot of effort
to make you believe.

00:07:24.870 --> 00:07:27.360
Once you come into contact with it,
you will become addicted.

00:07:27.920 --> 00:07:29.510
I clearly saw you drink it.

00:07:29.800 --> 00:07:31.680
Every time you brought the porridge,

00:07:32.680 --> 00:07:34.510
I had someone change it on the way.

00:07:35.160 --> 00:07:36.390
Even if I took a sip,

00:07:36.500 --> 00:07:37.780
I would spit it out immediately.

00:07:38.560 --> 00:07:39.750
So that's how it is.

00:07:41.360 --> 00:07:43.240
It was my mistake.

00:07:49.510 --> 00:07:50.350
Feng!

00:07:53.070 --> 00:07:53.910
Lady Cui,

00:07:54.300 --> 00:07:55.560
